# ─── Local development overview ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy the files below and fill in your values:
#   backend/.env          ← Express API (Render in production)
#   frontend/.env.local     ← Next.js app (Netlify in production)
#
# Run locally (two terminals):
#   npm run dev:backend     → http://localhost:4000
#   npm run dev:frontend    → http://localhost:3000
#
# Database (Neon):
#   1. Create a project at https://neon.tech
#   2. Copy the connection string into backend/.env as DATABASE_URL
#   3. Run migrations in database/migrations/ (000 first, then 001)
